Prepare uncooked tomato sauce. (see below) Cook pasta, drain, toss with olive oil, cool. Cook Grilled Fillets according to directions on package. In large bowl, combine sauce, pasta, feta cheese; toss gently. Cut Grilled Fillets into pieces and place on salad. To prepare Uncooked Tomato Sauce: Combine all ingredients in glass bowl. Cover: let stand at room temperature for 1 hour before tossing with pasta.